name: MeningococcalDiseaseTestsForNeisseriaMeningitidisAntigen
title: Meningococcal Disease (Tests for Neisseria meningitidis Antigen)
purpose:
(Clinical Focus: This set of values contains codes for laboratory test names associated with detecting the presence of Neisseria meningitidis antigen),(Data Element Scope: Laboratory tests names that were ordered or observed.),(Inclusion Criteria: VSAC query: Neisseria meningitidis ag;  

LOINC search: 'Neisseria meningitidis Ag -panel -isolate'),(Exclusion Criteria: panel and isolate tests)
